   methods in the literature (vertical bar X vertical bar and vertical bar
   E-o vertical bar are the numbers of states and observable events in a
   plant, respectively). We also derive an upper bound for the value of k
   in strong k-step opacity, and propose an effective algorithm to
   determine the maximal value of k for a given plant. Finally, we note
   that enforcement of strong infinite- and k-step opacity can be
